item.title: Google Calendar
item.description: Keeping students (and yourself) organized is essential in online programs. Here’s a guide to best using Google Calendar with Slack. This guide focuses on integrating the calendar in D2L/Brightspace LMS with Slack via Google Calendar. (Content coming soon!)
